node.text: Work like you don't need the money. Adopt the pace of nature: her secret is patience. A man should always consider how much he has more than he wants
Always believe in what you do have faith your self the only advice you can get is yourself
Fact always believe God is at the end to settle all your worries

No one can make you feel inferior without your consent. It is better to remain silent at the risk of being thought a fool, than to talk and remove all doubt of it. The fool doth think he is wise, but the wise man knows himself to be a fool.
For beautiful eyes, look for the good in others; for beautiful lips, speak only words of kindness; and for poise, walk with the knowledge that you are never alone.
